{"tid":2010431,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"現場手足唔該唔好再對啲撲完冰EQ低既垃圾撚狗","createTime":"2020-05-10T11:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T13:32:03.000Z","uid":41389,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bf0c890b2af1eb26d189b9f7956f4bfb86cde6a1","tid":2010431,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:42:58.000Z","msg":"你講野搞到佢唔開心 <br />\n見到幾個手足咩都無做單人屌狗比人拘捕 瞬間失去戰鬥能力<br />\n佢可以用盡一切方法搞鳩你 <br />\n佢可以老屈你 可以打鳩你 <br />\n單枝公勢力薄弱講少啲撚狗野 你就算無犯法你激鳩佢地佢地都會拉鳩你<br />\n記住 佢地自己都講左 佢毅進佢無野可以輸<br />\n要智勝 唔想比人查罰2000 同佢講句「警察加油 支持你地」<br />\n佢地班傻閪就會上撚曬電射撚埋精<br />\n無謂係無反擊之力之下用挑畔搞到自己扣血"},{"pid":"ecbf3efa53cfd04e1ec948ebfaba2dc4ec71275f","tid":2010431,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"打online game都知 挑畔係夠揪疊馬先用"},{"pid":"f737c7281cd4d0e2eb3a5fa9b008cf1a2c7ff62d","tid":2010431,"uid":21170,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:44:37.000Z","msg":"推，唔好盲目屌，有時為安全係要放低尊嚴"},{"pid":"808eaff1595aecb0793b8d48bca2b10c9dbadc47","tid":2010431,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ccf4d195c2137bdbccd96967aaa7dc213e0902","tid":2010431,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f737c7281cd4d0e2eb3a5fa9b008cf1a2c7ff62d","tid":2010431,"uid":21170,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:44:37.000Z","msg":"推，唔好盲目屌，有時為安全係要放低尊嚴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:46:19.000Z","msg":"都唔係要你放低尊嚴 佢地鍾意聽咪當餵下狗糧佢地更加high"},{"pid":"8134c0f1c6093f4e59a5cb352c1763781908c1ee","tid":2010431,"uid":21170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69ccf4d195c2137bdbccd96967aaa7dc213e0902","tid":2010431,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f737c7281cd4d0e2eb3a5fa9b008cf1a2c7ff62d","tid":2010431,"uid":21170,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:44:3